-- Webpack nace para ser el empaquetador de react de Facebook


4 Conceptos:
- Entry
- Outputs
- loader (Cargadores)
- Plugins



--Iniciar un proyecto
npm init -y

--instalar dependencias

npm i -D webpack webpack-dev-server babel-loader babel-cli babel-preset-es2015


###https://docs.npmjs.com/cli/install
#Comands Node
=> npm install 
    - in global mode : -g or --global   
    - will install all modules as dependencies in package.json
    - will the --production, npm will not intalls modules listed in devDependencies

=>  npm install save any specified packages into dependencies:
    + -P, --save-prod: Package will appear in your "dependencies".
    
    + -D, --save-dev: Package will appear in your "devDependencies"
    + -O, --save-optional: Package will appear in your "optionalDependencies"
    

###
WebPack config json
- webpack -w o webpack --wacht   : Esto te permite transpilar automaticamente los cambios.


#loader : Ejecutar codigo CSS
    - npm install style-loader css-loader -D
    - npm i -D style-loader css-loader



#Curso de Webpack

Instalar NPM  y webpack
=> npm install --global webpack webpack-cli

=> npm init
=> npm i -D webpack webpack-cli
=> npm run [build]